              "displayName": "Peng Zhang",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Asia/Shanghai"
            },
            "body": "Thanks [~kasha]\nI agreed with \"have a preemption priority or even a preemption cost per container\". \n\nAnd in my temporary fix, I preempt latest scheduled container instead of low or high priority containers. \nI think this will make containers for a mount of resources(at least steady fair share) steady. So MapReduce job progress will proceed. ",
            "updateAuthor": {
